# Applies to the worker build (deploy/worker.Dockerfile, context: repo root).
# The website/app builds use their own subdir contexts and are unaffected.
# Keep packages/execution/vendor (the emdash submodule) — it is required.
**/node_modules
.git
.github
.claude
website
app
design-system
docs
**/*.test.ts
**/dist
**/.DS_Store
*.bundle
# Never bake secrets / local credentials into the image (COPY . . context).
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks
**/*.p12
**/credentials*.json
**/service-account*.json
**/*.secret
